>Description:
For awhile I've noticed that when I select text (and cause it to hi-light), periodically some portion of what I've selected wont be highlighted. 
Here is an example that always is mis-highlighted 
(eq? (level) 'intermediate)
When I try to select this entire s-expression, only the portion from v to the last ) is colored black (all of it is selected when I cut, copy, etc).

>How-To-Repeat:
Type
(eq? (level) 'intermediate)
Begin selecting the text at the first (
Note that the first portion is no longer hi-lighted once you have passed the 
space between the first ) and the '
